          "bodyHtml": "<p>Dear ,</p><p><br></p><p>Ramadan Kareem 🌙</p><p><br></p><p>Thank you for your interest in the free Ramadan webinar presented by SBS – Sustainable Business Solutions.</p><p>We are delighted to invite you to join our upcoming session.</p><p><br></p><p>Business Psychology &amp; Organizational Behavior</p><p><br></p><p>Presented by:</p><p>Dr. Ibraheem El-Ashy</p><p>Executive Managing Partner at SBS</p><p>L&amp;D and Organizational Performance Development Advisor</p><p><br></p><p>📅 Wednesday, 4 March 2026</p><p>⏰ 9:00 PM – 11:00 PM</p><p><br></p><p>In this webinar, we will explore why organizations sometimes struggle to achieve the expected levels of performance despite having skilled employees and available resources. The session will focus on understanding employees’ psychological needs, the impact of workplace psychology on performance, building psychologically safe work environments, and how organizational behavior directly influences engagement and productivity.</p><p><br></p><p>🎓 Attendance is free as part of the Lead With Purpose Ramadan Series presented by SBS.</p><p>A certificate of attendance will be provided after the webinar.</p><p><br></p><p>Registration Link: [Add Registration Link Here]</p><p><br></p><p>We look forward to your attendance and hope you have an insightful and valuable session with us.</p><p><br></p><p>Warm regards,</p><p>SBS – Sustainable Business Solutions</p>",
